               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the second half of the year (fols.
                     2ra-185vc)&#xD; I-1) Maggābit (fols. 2ra-32vc)&#xD; I-2) Miyāzyā (fols.
                     33ra-57rb)&#xD; I-3) Gǝnbot (fols. 58ra-84vc)&#xD; I-4) Sane (fols.
                     85ra-114vb)&#xD; I-5) Ḥamle (fols. 115ra-153va)&#xD; I-6) Naḥāse (fols.
                     154ra-180vc)&#xD; I-7) Ṗagʷǝmen (fols. 181ra-185vc)&#xD; The commemoration
                     notes are followed by ʿarke-hymns&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-5;
                     colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
